
<h1>Downloads</h1>

<p>Here you will find links to download the all the Icelandic Sagas in various formats, such as EPUB and PDF. Markup-formatted files are XHTML strict, while plain text files are UTF-8 encoded. To read the sagas online, visit the <a href="/index_az.html">Saga Index page</a>. Individual saga texts can be downloaded on their respective pages.</p>

<p><a href="/files/zip/all_sagas_html.zip"><strong>XHTML</strong></a><br>
All the sagas in strict XHTML (UTF-8)</p>

<p><a href="/files/zip/all_sagas_text.zip"><strong>TEXT</strong></a><br>
All the sagas as plain text in UTF-8 encoding</p>

<p><a href="/files/zip/all_sagas_pdf.zip"><strong>PDF</strong></a><br>
All the sagas as PDF documents with a content index.</p>

<p><a href="/files/zip/all_sagas_epub.zip"><strong>EPUB</strong></a><br>
All sagas in EPUB format for electronic book-readers</p>

